  "cloudTutorialStep2Desc": "BeeCount Cloud does NOT offer self-registration (to prevent abuse on public servers). If you self-host: the first Docker boot prints a random admin email + password to the logs — use that. Joining someone else's server: ask the admin to create an account for you in Web → Users.",
